            "name": "Valse of Bloom and Blight",
            "desc": "<size=40><color=Title>Crimson Blossom<\/color><\/size>nAttack the target, dealing <color=Dark>Havoc DMG<\/color> (considered Basic Attack DMG), then enter <color=Highlight>Blossom Mode<\/color>.nThis attack can be performed in mid-air.n<size=10> <\/size>n<size=40><color=Title>Blossom Mode<\/color><\/size>n- Unable to move while suspended on vines.n- <color=Highlight>Basic Attack<\/color> and Heavy Attack <color=Highlight>Pruning<\/color> are replaced by Basic Attack <color=Highlight>Vining Waltz<\/color>: chain together 4 consecutive attacks, dealing <color=Dark>Havoc DMG<\/color>, considered Basic Attack DMG.n- When performing <color=Highlight>Vining Waltz Stage 3<\/color>, hold <color=Highlight>Normal Attack Button<\/color> to cast <color=Highlight>Blazing Waltz<\/color> that deals <color=Dark>Havoc DMG<\/color> before automatically performing <color=Highlight>Vining Waltz Stage 4<\/color>.n- <color=Highlight>Dodge Counter<\/color> is replaced by Dodge Counter <color=Highlight>Atonement<\/color>. {Cus:Ipt,Touch=Tap PC=Press Gamepad=Press} <color=Highlight>Normal Attack Button<\/color> right after a successful <color=Highlight>Dodge<\/color> to attack the target, dealing <color=Dark>Havoc DMG<\/color>, considered Basic Attack DMG.n- Resonance Skill is replaced by Resonance Skill <color=Highlight>Floral Ravage<\/color>. Casting <color=Highlight>Floral Ravage<\/color> deals <color=Dark>Havoc DMG<\/color>, considered Basic Attack DMG.n- Resonance Skill <color=Highlight>Floral Ravage<\/color> can be cast in mid-air.n- <color=Highlight>Blossom Mode<\/color> ends after casting Resonance Skill <color=Highlight>Floral Ravage<\/color>.n- <color=Highlight>Blossom Mode<\/color> ends after using the <color=Highlight>Levitator<\/color>.n- Jump is replaced with Basic Attack <color=Highlight>Vining Ronde<\/color>. {Cus:Ipt,Touch=Tap PC=Press Gamepad=Press} Jump to attack the target at the cost of STA, dealing <color=Dark>Havoc DMG<\/color> (considered Basic Attack DMG). This ends the <color=Highlight>Blossom Mode<\/color>.n- Using Basic Attack <color=Highlight>Vining Waltz<\/color> and Basic Attack <color=Highlight>Blazing Waltz<\/color> in mid-air consumes STA.n- Casting Resonance Skill <color=Highlight>Floral Ravage<\/color> doesn't restore STA.n- Consume STA continuously to stay suspended on the vines."
