            "name": "Vegetative Universe",
            "desc": "Hitting a target with <color=Highlight>Normal Attack<\/color>, Basic Attack <color=Highlight>Vining Waltz<\/color>, Basic Attack <color=Highlight>Blazing Waltz<\/color>, Basic Attack <color=Highlight>Vining Ronde<\/color>, Dodge Counter <color=Highlight>Atonement <\/color>, Resonance Skill <color=Highlight>Crimson Blossom<\/color>, and Resonance Skill <color=Highlight>Floral Ravage<\/color> consumes Crimson Pistils. The Energy Regen Multiplier of this attack is increased by 150%.nConsuming 10 Crimson Pistils recovers 4 Concerto Energy and obtains <SapTag=3>1<\/SapTag> {Cus:Sap,S=Crimson Bud P=Crimson Buds SapTag=3}. Each bud lasts for 15s, stacking up to 10 times.n<size=10> <\/size>n<size=40><color=Title>Forte Circuit: Ephemeral<\/color><\/size>nWhen Concerto Energy is fully recovered, and <color=Highlight>Ephemeral<\/color> is not on Cooldown, Resonance Skill is replaced with <color=Highlight>Ephemeral<\/color>.nCasting <color=Highlight>Ephemeral<\/color> consumes 70 Concerto Energy and deals <color=Dark>Havoc DMG<\/color> to the targets. This damage is considered Basic Attack DMG.nCamellya enters <color=Highlight>Budding Mode<\/color> after casting <color=Highlight>Ephemeral<\/color>.nThis can be cast in mid-air.n<size=10> <\/size>n<size=40><color=Title>Budding Mode<\/color><\/size>n- <color=Highlight>Sweet Dream<\/color>: Increase the DMG Multiplier of <color=Highlight>Normal Attack<\/color>, Basic Attack <color=Highlight>Vining Waltz<\/color>, Basic Attack <color=Highlight>Blazing Waltz<\/color>, Basic Attack <color=Highlight>Vining Ronde<\/color>, Dodge Counter <color=Highlight>Atonement<\/color>, Resonance Skill <color=Highlight>Crimson Blossom<\/color>, and Resonance Skill <color=Highlight>Floral Ravage<\/color> by 50%.n- Casting <color=Highlight>Ephemeral<\/color> consumes all Crimson Buds. Each Crimson Bud consumed additionally increases the DMG Multiplier of <color=Highlight>Sweet Dream<\/color> by 5%, up to 50%. n- When in <color=Highlight>Budding Mode<\/color>, Camellya cannot gain Crimson Buds.n- When in <color=Highlight>Budding Mode<\/color>, the Energy Regen Multiplier of <color=Highlight>Normal Attack<\/color>, Basic Attack <color=Highlight>Vining Waltz<\/color>, Basic Attack <color=Highlight>Blazing Waltz<\/color>, Basic Attack <color=Highlight>Vining Ronde<\/color>, Dodge Counter <color=Highlight>Atonement<\/color>, Resonance Skill <color=Highlight>Crimson Blossom<\/color>, and Resonance Skill <color=Highlight>Floral Ravage<\/color> is reduced to 0%.n- <color=Highlight>Budding Mode<\/color> ends when Camellya is switched off the field.n- <color=Highlight>Budding Mode<\/color> ends when all Crimson Pistils are consumed.n<size=10> <\/size>n<size=40><color=Title>Crimson Pistil<\/color><\/size>nCamellya can hold up to 100 Crimson Pistils.n- Casting Intro Skill <color=Highlight>Everblooming<\/color> recovers 100 Crimson Pistils.n- Activating Forte Circuit's <color=Highlight>Ephemeral<\/color> recovers 100 Crimson Pistils."
